{"type": "article", "id": 49020, "title": "病号服不仅要好看，还要便于医生做检查｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-08T23:23:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 43320, "name": "Off-White"}, {"id": 46884, "name": "Neutrogena"}, {"id": 32548, "name": "Pulpo"}, {"id": 46885, "name": "Care + Wear"}, {"id": 46886, "name": "Pilar Torcal"}, {"id": 46887, "name": "Yves Behar"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180108210536zI46kyj9bqvrGQ3f.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Hospital Gown by Parsons students with Care + Wear</h3><p>帕森斯设计学院（Parsons School of Design）的学生，与医护服生产公司 Care+Wear 合作，推出了一款新病服，设计灵感源自日本和服，采用交领设计，在衣服内外侧、袖口、背面等不同位置设计了绳带或纽扣，背后还设有防护褶，仅用一款便可替代五种不同类型的病号服，在病人需要进行不同身体部位的检查时，可以同时方便病人与医生。售价 45 美元，<a href=\"https://www.careandwear.com/products/patient-gown\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210608C9pB20J3wXHSiKUd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.075064\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210608xRgSMrulO3VAboCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210607KsSFhgfZ6T0ABQwL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210608f80rKeoAjEkGXZzD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210610GHmnA6IKEwSUjf0V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801082106109sSBRQCn1Md0Wh8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Stellar lamps by Sebastian Herkner for Pulpo</h3><p>Sebastian Herkner 为德国品牌 Pulpo 设计了一系列球形玻璃吊灯，据称灵感源自通过望远镜看到的星星。Stellar 系列包括大、中、小三个尺寸，每个灯由两个水平或者垂直链接的玻璃半球组成，一半是喷砂处理的磨砂质地表面，一半是纹理清晰的弯曲的凸脊，试图引发人们关于月球表面的联想。</p><p>当然，你还能过看到玻璃灯罩上不同的气泡、条纹和其他尺寸、颜色的变化，这都是手工制作过程会产生的结果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801082107338xa1c4jSWhEo6GPs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210734W6klgoLy09pNOtqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210735ZgjwhbpY79DISrBc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.719120\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210735UG2Bcq40iEuL9IAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Skin360 by Neutrogena</h3><p>随着生活水平的提升，人们越来越关注自己的皮肤状态。在本周的 CES 2018 大会上，护肤品品牌 Neutrogena 将发布一款皮肤扫描设备 Skin360，它可通过 iPhone 检测皮肤健康，还可通过人工智能技术，测试皮肤得分并指导如何保持健康皮肤。</p><p>Skin360 像是手机微距、广角可拆卸镜头，它可直接套用在苹果手机背后，然后将摄像头对准皮肤即可，内置 12 枚 LED 灯和一个 30 倍放大镜，能将皮肤表面画面放大，同时还可以测量皮肤水份，皱纹和毛孔等。它配合 APP，可以帮助用户快速分析出自己皮肤的健康程度，还可通过人工智能技术将测试者皮肤和年龄跟其他用户比较和评分，并指导用户如何保持皮肤健康。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210854r7AmDM0RUKNbvs95.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.975550\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801082108547CDxT1mXKye8drth.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210855t6djMvHyX3lzqYWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210854zPlcH9A2vCd0mFUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210855ftHXL2pnRw05CrQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.035452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hive View by Yves Behar</h3><p>这是一款室内摄像头，出自瑞士知名工业设计师 Yves Behar 之手。它的把手非常特别，轻质摄像头能够与其超轻的底座拆分开，将其安装在墙壁、书架或磁铁支架上。</p><p>Hive View 的三部分均可旋转或弯曲，实现 130 度的视野范围，共有两种颜色搭配可供选择：黑色与红铜色组合以及白色与香槟金组合。此外，Hive View 配备有高清视频直播、人像检测与摄像历史功能，可随时随地获取。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210927iEml2fBRtucMx9C4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210927ta6XpVjBKSNlHTq1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210927fcjo6WXNkIBlr9Y8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801082109276PWcnBJtdmKaYXvz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650367\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210927m6gZj3T0xLbY8PyD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643032\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108210927NrkBa2msSYdKlzTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FIRETAPE Mask by Off-White</h3><p>冬季出街，一款酷酷的口罩可能会是吸睛神器。来看这款街头潮牌 Off-White 的单品，围绕秋冬主题 FIRETAPE 推出的口窄，以传统口罩为基础，分别在纯黑、纯白色口罩上加入这一季全新的“ FIRE LINE DO NOT CROSS ”封条胶带图案，这是继 Industrial Belt、斜条纹元素后，再次展现品牌带有工业色彩的元素。售价 84 美元，<a href=\"https://www.off---white.com/en/US/men/products/omrg001s181851091060#image-0\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108211039UbZfVoDvnaew3XqT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801082110397l0bdrvpD6uGoY1X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vibrant, illustrated calendar by Pilar Torcal</h3><p>Pilar Torcal 是一位来自巴塞罗那的跨学科平面设计师和插画家，曾经梦想成为一名体操运动员和考古学家。不过，当她意识到色彩和平面设计才是真正的兴趣所在后，她把注意力转向了广告和公关。这个可爱的插图日历是她的新作，活泼明丽的配色和不规则的几何形状的碰撞，成为这款日历最引人注目的部分。她希望给人新一年带去积极的展望。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108211155He8Qzdf0l5pPvyiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684545\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108211156yuoMVHEfxPCmNlRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.285455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108211157PzxoEa51DgWOpTKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.285455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108211157Uw78Q0MymLpdJNkO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.285455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108211157XuJ0UVI82fly4Fia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.141818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}